   "source": [
    "print(\"=\"*60)\n",
    "print(\"FINAL DELIVERABLE\")\n",
    "print(\"=\"*60)\n",
    "print(result[\"final_output\"])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Key Takeaways\n",
    "\n",
    "| Concept | Implementation |\n",
    "|---------|---------------|\n",
    "| **3-tier hierarchy** | Strategic sets goals → Tactical plans tasks → Execution does work |\n",
    "| **Information flows down** | Each tier passes refined context to the next |\n",
    "| **Isolation** | Workers don't need to understand the big picture — only their task |\n",
    "| **Scalability** | Add more workers or departments without redesigning the upper layers |\n",
    "\n",
    "## What's Next\n",
    "\n",
    "**Notebook 12** closes the loop with **LLM-as-a-Judge** — a systematic evaluation framework that scores agent outputs across all our notebooks using a structured rubric."
   ]
  }
